# Tarball exclusions for @windyroad/architect.
# The package.json `files` field is the inclusion allowlist (bin/, agents/,
# hooks/, skills/, scripts/, .claude-plugin/, lib/). This `.npmignore` denies
# matches at finer granularity for paths that should not ship to adopters.
#
# Per ADR-075 (Amendment 2026-06-02) Confirmation criterion: SKILL eval
# configs + fixtures must NOT ship in the published tarball. Verify with
# `npm pack --dry-run` from packages/architect/ — no path matching
# skills/*/eval/ should appear. Mirrors packages/itil/.npmignore precedent
# (Phase 3 capture-problem SKILL eval).
#
# NOTE: the load-bearing exclusion is the `"!skills/*/eval/"` negation in
# package.json `files:` array — npm honours `files:` negation patterns
# before consulting .npmignore. This `.npmignore` is the belt-and-braces
# safety net for any future per-directory drift.
#
# @adr ADR-075 (Amendment 2026-06-02)
# @rfc RFC-012 S6
# @problem P324 (Phase 4 — create-adr SKILL eval)
skills/*/eval/
